  title: Scarface
  genre: Drama 2
  position: 35
  description: After getting a green card in exchange for assassinating a Cuban government
    official, Tony Montana stakes a claim on the drug trade in Miami. Viciously murdering
    anyone who stands in his way, Tony eventually becomes the biggest drug lord in
    the state, controlling nearly all the cocaine that comes through Miami. But increased
    pressure from the police, wars with Colombian drug cartels and his own drug-fueled
    paranoia serve to fuel the flames of his eventual downfall.
  coverArt: {fileID: -1391461048, guid: 63c8c566a89a73948be73adfe17277fe, type: 3}
